Mexico ' s TIIE 28 - day rate falls to 20 . 22 pct . Mexico ' s 28 - day interbank interest rate for Friday , July 18 , was fixed at 20 . 22 percent , or 76 basis points lower than the July 17 rate of 20 . 98 percent , Banco de Mexico said on Thursday . The 28 - day TIIE is a market - weighted average interbank rate , revised each working day . It is valid for the day after it is set . The new rate will be published in Friday ' s edition of the Mexican government ' s Official Gazette . ( ( - - Mexico City newsroom + 525 728 - 9558 ) ) 
